( '17', 'Ross', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-07-12 11:52:17', '2024-08-16 11:38:31', 'https://500m.in/images/uploads/attachment/1723808302.jpg', '5 - 2.5k', 'Online', 'PhD in Law', '3500', '99', '<p>Im Ross Johnson, a PhD graduate and experienced law tutor dedicated to providing expert writing assistance with reports, essays, and dissertations. With a strong background in law and a commitment to excellence, I ensure each project is meticulously crafted to meet your specific needs. My passion for legal education drives me to help students navigate the complexities of legal studies with confidence and clarity.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Whether you require help with research, structuring your essay, or polishing your dissertation, I am here to support you every step of the way. My services include:</p><ul><li>Assisting with legal research and analysis to ensure your work is comprehensive and accurate.</li><li>Structuring essays and reports to enhance clarity and coherence.</li><li>Polishing dissertations to meet academic standards and impress your evaluators.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Throughout my career, I have gained extensive experience in tutoring and mentoring students, enabling them to excel in their academic endeavors. My approach is student-centered, focusing on your unique needs and learning style to provide tailored support.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Lets work together to elevate your writing and academic achievements. Reach out today to get started on your next project and unlock your full potential in legal studies. Dont let academic stress hold you back  let me help you achieve the success you deserve.</p>', 'English', '36,34,33,32,30,16,12', NULL, NULL, 'active', 'Essay', '2500', '24', '1', 'Educrafter' ),
