( '15', 'Educrafter', 'How it works', NULL, '<h1 style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:3pt;" class=""><span style="font-size:26pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Get Your Essay Now!</span></h1><h1 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:20pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size:20pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">See How We Make It Happen</span></h1><p><b style="font-weight:normal;" id="docs-internal-guid-8bb35b84-7fff-72e1-2c9e-474e20b0a954"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Step 1: Provide your order information</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Sign up on EduCrafter and create your account. Fill out our order form by providing all relevant details about your order, such as assignment type, number of pages, writing level, deadline, preferred writer (if you have any), etc. Enter these details accurately to receive an accurate paper.</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Step 2: Make the payment</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Upon completion of your order details, please proceed to make your payment for the order. We provide various secure payment options, including credit cards, debit cards, and other payment gateways. Once the payment is completed and the order gets processed, a writer will be assigned.</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Step 3: Get an exceptional paper</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">The writer starts working on your requirements as soon as they get your requirements. Your paper will be promptly delivered to you, based on the deadline you provided. Upon receiving the paper, you may review it and check if it meets your expectations. If you need a revision, feel free to contact us.&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br><br></b></p><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:6pt;" class=""><span style="font-size:16pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Get Flawless Assignments On Time!</span></h2><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Never miss your assignment deadline with EduCrafter!</span></p><p><br></p>', 'Learn How It Works - Affordable and Fast - EduCrafter', 'how it work', 'how-it-works', 'Learn how educrafter. co provides speedy, cost-effective essay writing help. Streamline your academic journey with our straightforward process', NULL, '1', '2024-04-27 04:15:51', '2024-04-30 10:39:58', NULL ),
