ext-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">We understand that revisions may be necessary to ensure your complete satisfaction. However, whenever a claim is made or a refund request is initiated, EduCrafter will perform a thorough verification of such claims/requests. Thus, the response to such requests will be made based on the verification results.&nbsp;</span></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">Also, note that while we deliver high-quality essays, we cannot guarantee specific grades on your assignments.&nbsp; Grades depend on various factors beyond our control. However, we are committed to your academic success and may be able to offer assistance with your next order.</span></p><p><br><br></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;">To ensure a prompt resolution, all refund requests must be submitted within 30 days of receiving your completed paper. Requests submitted after 30 days may be considered for a partial account credit, subject to review of your specific situation.</span></p>', 'Money-Back Guarantee - Risk-Free Essay Services at Educrafter', NULL, 'money-back-guarantee', 'Learn about our Money-Back Guarantee at Educrafter. Enjoy risk-free essay writing services with our promise of satisfaction or your money back', NULL, '1', '2024-04-30 07:19:55', '2024-04-30 10:45:54', NULL ),
