yle="color: var(--blue-normal);">Faking data, information, or citations.</span></span></li><li><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: var(--blue-normal);">Taking tests, quizzes, engaging in cheating, plagiarism, or any activities that violate your school, college, or university\'s academic policies. If the Expert knowingly facilitates cheating, they will be removed from our Site.</span></span></li></ul><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;"></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">Non-compliance with the guidelines specified in this Code will lead to an immediate and permanent ban from our Site, with no possibility of account recovery.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;"><br></p><h2 style="margin-bottom: 30px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 80px; font-size: 36px; line-height: 43.2px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;">COMPLIANCE WITH LAWS AND REGULATIONS</h2><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">You must adhere to all applicable laws, regulations, and academic institution guidelines when using our Service. We reserve the right to refuse Service to anyone who violates these requirements.</p><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">By using our Service in violation of this Code, you acknowledge that you may be