 font-weight: 700; margin-top: 80px; font-size: 36px; line-height: 43.2px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;">CHANGES TO THIS CODE</h2><p style="margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 27px; color: rgb(14, 16, 26); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">Kindly be aware that this Code may undergo changes without advance notice. It is your duty to periodically review the Code to remain informed about any modifications. Your use of our Service implies that you have read, comprehended, and accepted the regulations delineated in this Code.</p><br><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Order Cancellation&nbsp;</span></h2><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">If you choose to cancel your order after it has been paid for and assigned to a writer, the refund amount will depend on the progress made at the time of cancellation. Our team will assess the work completed and determine a fair refund percentage based on our policy. In the rare case that we need to cancel your order, you will be notified immediately and receive a full refund. Read more about our Money-back guarantee.</span></p><br><h2 dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:18pt;margin-bottom:6pt;"><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Resource Materials</span></h2><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Writers at EduCrafter prioritize using the most relevant and reliable sources for research paper assignments. However, we encourage customers to provide any specific resources they would like the writer to consider. If a requested resource isn\'t readily available to the writer, we\'ll kindly ask the customer to upload it through their account or profile page.</span></p><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Promptly providing any requested resources helps ensure the order\'s timely completion.</span></p><br><p dir="ltr" style="line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Please note that delays caused by late resource uploads may impact the delivery timeframe. In such cases, EduCrafter cannot be held responsible for the tardiness.<