( '73', '19', 'Can You Rewrite My Paper?', 'Yes, we can absolutely rewrite your paper and deliver it to you on time. Please give us your requirements through our order form and make the necessary payment to get us started. Upon reviewing your order, our team will assign a suitable writer who can work on rewriting your essay.', '2024-05-03 04:36:05', '2024-05-03 04:36:05' ),
( '74', '19', 'How Fast to Rewrite My Paper?', 'Usually, it depends on the length of the paper. Our writers get started with the rewriting process as soon as they are assigned to your task. However, the whole process of rewriting will depend on numerous parameters, such as the length of the essay, the complexity of the topic, and the deadline. Nonetheless, we promise to deliver it on time.', '2024-05-03 04:36:05', '2024-05-03 04:36:05' ),
( '75', '19', 'Who Will Rewrite My Essay?', 'We have professional writers and editors in our team and they will rewrite the essay. Once you fill out the information on the order form, such as subject, task type, task topic, and academic level, we will assign an appropriate writer. Rest assured, all our writers are experienced and well-qualified for the task.', '2024-05-03 04:36:05', '2024-05-03 04:36:05' ),
( '76', '19', 'Can You Rewrite Essay Texts Confidentially?', 'Yes, we maintain confidentiality and never disclose or share your personal details or essay texts with any other external parties. We are a professional service provider and we prioritize the security and data privacy of our clients. Rest assured, you can submit your personal information and order details without a second thought.', '2024-05-03 04:36:05', '2024-05-03 04:36:05' ),
( '77', '19', 'Can you rewrite my essay for me once again if I don\'t like the first draft?', 'Yes, EduCrafter provides a revision request facility for all the customers to get amendments done. In case, you need changes or your requirements get changed and you want us to rework the same essay, you can place a revision request. Once the request gets processed, the writer will rework it.', '2024-05-03 04:36:05', '2024-05-03 04:36:05' ),
( '94', '44', 'How can EduCrafter help me with my essay writing?', '<p>EduCrafter offers personalized essay writing support services to empower students like you.  Our team of experienced essay writers can assist with various writing tasks, including essays, case studies, and dissertations, across a wide range of subjects. We work closely with you to understand your specific requirements and ensure the delivered content is original and meets your academic needs.<br></p>', '2024-05-09 15:23:29', '2024-05-09 15:23:29' ),
( '95', '44', 'What are the benefits of using EduCrafter\'s services?', '<p data-sourcepos="13:1-13:55">There are several benefits to using EduCrafter:</p><p>
INSERT INTO `service_faq`(`id`,`service_id`,`question`,`answer`,`created_at`,`updated_at`) VALUES 
( '323', '38', 'Will My Essay Be Free from Plagiarism and AI?', '<p><strong>Plagiarism-Free Guarantee:</strong> EduCrafter guarantees plagiarism-free essays. We utilize advanced plagiarism and AI-detection tools to ensure the originality and quality of every paper we deliver. Your essay will undergo rigorous checks to meet our strict standards<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2024-07-22 13:21:17', '2024-07-22 13:21:17' ),
( '324', '38', 'How Does EduCrafter Protect My Privacy?', '<p><strong>Your Privacy is Paramount:</strong> We take data security seriously. We utilize strict security measures to safeguard your personal information and guarantee complete confidentiality throughout the entire process.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '2024-07-22 13:21:17', '2024-07-22 13:21:17' ),
( '352', '30', 'Who Are Our Essay Writers?', '<p><strong>Experienced &amp; Certified: </strong>EduCrafter\'s essay writers are confirmed native English speakers with years of writing experience and a strong academic background. All hold Master\'s or Ph.D. degrees from top universities, ensuring exceptional writing skills and subject knowledge.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '353', '30', 'Can You Find an Essay Writer for Any Subject?', '<p><br>Yes! We have a vast pool of experienced <a href="https://educrafter.co/tutors">essay writers </a>across various disciplines, including complex subjects like Physics, Engineering, and Information Technology. No matter your topic, we can find the perfect writer to assist you.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '354', '30', 'Can My Paper Writer Make Changes to the Final Version?', '<p><strong>Free Unlimited Revisions</strong>: We strive for 100% customer satisfaction. Even after you receive your completed essay, you can request free and unlimited revisions to ensure it meets your expectations perfectly.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '355', '30', 'How Can I Be Sure My Essay is Original?', '<p><strong>Guaranteed Originality:</strong> At EduCrafter, plagiarism is unacceptable. We craft all essays from scratch and meticulously check them for uniqueness using advanced detection tools. Every order includes a free originality report for your peace of mind.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '356', '30', 'How Fast Can You Deliver My Essay?', '<p><strong>We Deliver When You Need It:</strong> EduCrafter offers flexible deadlines to meet your needs.</p><p><strong>Standard Delivery:</strong> For most essays, our writers can deliver high-quality work within 4-5 business days. This timeframe allows for thorough<a href="https://educrafter.co/research-paper-writing-service"> research, writing</a>, and editing.</p><p><strong>Rush Delivery:</strong> Need your essay sooner? We can accommodate tighter deadlines as fast as 12 hours. However, for rush orders, the complexity of the topic may affect the final quality.</p><p><strong>Complex Assignments:</strong> For lengthy or particularly complex papers, a longer timeframe is ideal. Contact us beforehand to discuss your project and ensure your writer has <strong>ample time </strong>(10-15 business days) for in-depth research and analysis.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '357', '30', 'Will My Essay Writer Follow My Instructions?', '<p>Absolutely! Your satisfaction is our priority. Our professional writers meticulously review your instructions before crafting your essay. They\'ll ensure your requirements are met and deliver an impactful piece that reflects your needs. Additionally, you can discuss further details with your assigned writer through our one-on-one chat feature.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '358', '30', 'Will I Be Able To Communicate with My Essay Writer?', '<p>Yes, you can communicate with your<a href="https://educrafter.co/book-report-help"> report writer </a>at EduCrafter. Once your order is processed and a writer is assigned, you will have the opportunity to stay in touch with your writer. You can chat with the writer and discuss your report requirements in detail.</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '359', '30', 'How Do I Receive My Finished Essay?', '<p><strong>Easy Download &amp; Support:</strong> Once completed, your essay will be securely available for download from our website. Our friendly support team is always happy to assist you if you have any questions or require further help.<br>&nbsp;</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '360', '30', 'How Does EduCrafter Protect My Privacy?', '<p><strong>Your Privacy is Paramount:</strong> We take data security seriously. We utilize strict security measures to safeguard your personal information and guarantee complete confidentiality throughout the entire process.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '2024-09-02 08:29:55', '2024-09-02 08:29:55' ),
( '370', '42', 'How does the EduCrafter referral program work?', '<p>It\'s simple! Log in to EduCrafter, share your unique referral link with friends, and earn 50 for each friend who signs up and places their first order. Plus, your friend gets 50 off their first order too!</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '371', '42', 'How much can I earn from referrals?', '<p>Theres no limit! You earn 50 for each friend who signs up and places an order using your referral link. One of our students even earned 40,000 through referralsso your earning potential is unlimited!</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '372', '42', 'Is there a limit to the number of friends I can refer?', '<p>No, theres no limit! Refer as many friends as youd like and keep earning 50 for each successful referral.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '373', '42', 'How do I get rewarded?', '<p>Once your friend places their first order using your referral link, you\'ll receive 50, which you can withdraw or use toward your future order.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '374', '42', 'What qualifies as a successful referral?', '<p>A successful referral occurs when your referred friend signs up through your unique link and places their first order on EduCrafter. Once their order is completed, youll receive your 50.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '375', '42', 'How long does it take to receive my referral reward?', '<p>Referral credits are applied to your EduCrafter account instantly after your friends first order is successfully completed.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '376', '42', 'Can I track my referrals and rewards?', '<p>Yes! You can monitor all your referrals and rewards in the <strong>"Refer a Friend"</strong> section in My account. Youll be able to see how many friends have signed up and how much youve earned.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '377', '42', 'Do I need an EduCrafter account to refer friends?', '<p>Yes, you need an EduCrafter account to generate your unique referral link and track your rewards.</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' ),
( '378', '42', 'What if my friend forgets to use my referral link?', '<p>Unfortunately, to qualify for the 50 , your friend must use your unique referral link when signing up. Make sure to remind them!</p>', '2024-09-07 07:24:18', '2024-09-07 07:24:18' );
