ernal entities.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Processing the collected user information</span><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;">As mentioned above, EduCrafter never sells, rents, or shares the collected user information with third parties; instead, it is utilized for the following:</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Facilitate service utilization: </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Fulfilling the purpose of providing the desired services.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Internal administrative purpose: </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Covering record keeping, billing, market research, and accounting tasks.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Improve customer support:</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;"> Responding to the inquiries, complaints, and requests raised by customers.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Personalize service experience:</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;"> Customizing the content and/or layout of the Service.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Provide service updates:</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;"> Notifying the essential updates or changes pertaining to the service.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span style="color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Except as set out above, we will not sell, distribute, or disclose your Information without your consent, unless on occasions required or permitted by law, such as complying with a subpoena, or similar legal processes.</span><br></p><p><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b><span style="background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Plagiarism</span><b style="font-weight:normal;"><br></b></p><p><span style="color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Customers have the right to request revisions to ensure their satisfaction with the delivered work.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Plagiarism Guarantee: </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Our company maintains a strict plagiarism policy. We guarantee that content delivered through our writing services will exhibit a plagiarism level below 10%. In any case, if the delivered content exceeds this threshold, a full refund will be issued.</span><br></p><p><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(31, 31, 31); font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">Editing/Proofreading Disclaimer: </span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-ser