( '106', '46', 'How quickly can my essay be completed?', '<p><span style="color: rgb(13, 13, 13); font-family: Shne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; white-space-collapse: preserve;">While the timeframe for completing your essay depends on factors like length, complexity, and urgency, at EduCrafter, we aim to deliver high-quality essays within a timeframe that suits your needs. Rest assured, when you place your order, we are committed to meeting your deadline while upholding the highest standards of quality and excellence.</span><br></p>', '2024-05-10 09:22:52', '2024-05-10 09:22:52' ),
